<p>A wonderful Celtic smoke bottle in black marble. Made for burning incense sticks the bottle lid has a small drilled hole to insert your lit incense sticks. When placed back on top the incense then burns upward and the ash drops and is collected in the base. The patterned sides of the bottle have numerous small holes which let the smoke and aroma from the incense escape evenly while looking great. Dimensions- 310mm tall.</p>